Task 1

Creating Directory:

mkdir super_secret_stuff 

Creating File:

touch super_secret_stuff/top_secret.txt 

Updating Database:

sudo updatedb 

Saving Path to File:

locate top_secret.txt > ~/secret_place.txt 

Task 2

sudo find -maxdepth 4 -type f -size +1M -exec ls -lh {} \; | sort -k 5hr > ~/filesizes.txt 
